This app helps in emergency case during vehicle accident it immidiately informing your emergency contacts about your location by sending them SMS

various resources used:
LocationFinder.java from https://droidbyme.medium.com/get-current-location-using-gps-network-provider-d2915f2ec7a5
sensormanager      https://developer.android.com/reference/android/hardware/SensorManager.html
                  https://stackoverflow.com/questions/24732756/how-to-run-a-background-service-in-android-to-use-accelerometer
                  
services     https://developer.android.com/guide/components/services#java
